    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对“观察”类游戏的一种独特演绎。留意异常以推进你的一天，否则你将陷入无尽的循环。游戏时长为30到120分钟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被困在记忆的循环中。通过做出正确的选择，帮助自己消除记忆中的异常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/3d6ca6d5693c7edb4999e1a0e38c18bc.webp?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9305fdb36fe57d7094180aad89be5a51.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9305fdb36fe57d7094180aad89be5a51.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9305fdb36fe57d7094180aad89be5a51.mp4?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>规则</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏规则很简单:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你发现异常，离开你的房子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你没有发现异常，去睡觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/ce52a9c8190f221ea3cb62bb926ff0e6.webp?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=45 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9d0c50d3c39bafcf4597fafd126e9700.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9d0c50d3c39bafcf4597fafd126e9700.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9d0c50d3c39bafcf4597fafd126e9700.mp4?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正确选择才能推进一天。选错的话，你将从第1天重新开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到达第10天即可达到结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/22d83a8fc5bbd69fc29ad6a758dc2802.webp?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=45 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/a49d9f5835202f61c7d50025dc780e33.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/a49d9f5835202f61c7d50025dc780e33.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/a49d9f5835202f61c7d50025dc780e33.mp4?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS风格复古画面 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事丰富 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多重结局</p></li></ul>",
